5 年已開始製作具有水果皮質感的可食用杯子，而這次名為 Lolistraw 的飲管由一種新海藻類材料製成，更可以添加口味或是營養成分。公司聯合創辦人之一 Chelsea Briganti 說：「可以想像用香草或焦糖飲管喝冷泡咖啡。我們認為這有助於無塑膠運動，因為我們不是要求消費者完全不用飲管，而是為他們提供解決膠飲管危機的方案。消費者不用犧牲，亦能獲取樂趣，而這又可持續。」該公司計劃瞄準膠飲管目前使用量最高的場地，如體育館，快餐店、咖啡店或果汁店作推廣。飲管一個版本是無味的，看起來像膠飲管，而其他則有顏色及不同口味。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最多用者自付"},{"pid":"7eb392701d9ee819a9ed823a9a38a6c2b063e5fc","tid":590197,"uid":26752,"like":4,"dislike":5,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"611ad0947df208558f777309222b859786293599","tid":590197,"uid":24160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T14:59:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T18:01:47.000Z","msg":"唔好嬲<br />\n最多比呢條飲管過你<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d79c46b44ff55f3b53b017565581395abb8863d9","tid":590197,"uid":24160,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"9fe918a4f15569eae8c8169b0e8592a7acf2b5a0","tid":590197,"uid":51183,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"c4f2c054db43425a28641595dada3fad232fbfcf","tid":590197,"uid":24160,"like":17,"dislike":2,"score":15,"quote":{"pid":"b96059909da9bec4b0fc0464565c9333c82fb9af","tid":590197,"uid":64345,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T12:50:38.000Z","msg":"應該唔比賣凍飲"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T12:53:47.000Z","msg":"一係就design 杯嘢飲點樣唔用飲筒都飲得好<br />\n而唔係一味喺到ban on99<br />\n<br />\n又要要賣有cream, 有冰凍飲又要人唔用飲筒<br />\n<br />\n即係畀塊牛扒你 唔畀刀叉一鳩樣"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T17:53:09.000Z","msg":"用呢樣應該得<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.cup.com.hk/2017/12/07/eat-edible-straw/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cup.com.hk%2F2017%2F12%2F07%2Feat-edible-straw%